>> As I look across my body,
your planet, your home,

00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:12.300 align:middle line:84%
I hear your voices, the
cries for help, the grief,

00:01:12.300 --> 00:01:24.290 align:middle line:84%
and the sadness of loss,
the confusion, the ignoring.

00:01:24.290 --> 00:01:30.460 align:middle line:90%


00:01:30.460 --> 00:01:32.455 align:middle line:84%
I see people who
don't want to look.

00:01:32.455 --> 00:01:38.390 align:middle line:90%


00:01:38.390 --> 00:01:41.810 align:middle line:84%
I see people who
feel everything.

00:01:41.810 --> 00:01:47.440 align:middle line:90%


00:01:47.440 --> 00:01:49.705 align:middle line:90%
I see children who are confused.

00:01:49.705 --> 00:01:53.840 align:middle line:90%


00:01:53.840 --> 00:01:56.080 align:middle line:84%
