all their life in nature,

00:02:10.270 --> 00:02:14.260 align:middle line:90%
wondering what went wrong.

00:02:14.260 --> 00:02:21.040 align:middle line:90%


00:02:21.040 --> 00:02:32.960 align:middle line:84%
I see people in power,
turning their hearts cold,

00:02:32.960 --> 00:02:34.505 align:middle line:90%
