with tears and openness

00:02:58.870 --> 00:03:00.290 align:middle line:90%
and willingness to change.

00:03:00.290 --> 00:03:06.490 align:middle line:90%


00:03:06.490 --> 00:03:08.610 align:middle line:84%
I see the constraints
you've placed

00:03:08.610 --> 00:03:21.020 align:middle line:84%
