compromises, the challenges.

00:03:21.020 --> 00:03:28.050 align:middle line:90%


00:03:28.050 --> 00:03:30.390 align:middle line:84%
And I see the
beautiful expressions

00:03:30.390 --> 00:03:44.950 align:middle line:84%
of love, the people who create
small paradises in the hidden

00:03:44.950 --> 00:03:47.590 align:middle line:90%
corners of my body.

00:03:47.590 --> 00:03:52.800 align:middle line:90%


00:03:52.800 --> 00:03:53.720 align:middle line:90%
I see it all.

00:03:53.720 --> 00:03:58.100 align:middle line:90%


00:03:58.100 --> 00:04:02.225 align:middle line:84%
And I know you,
every one of you.

00:04:02.225 --> 00:04:12.460 align:middle line:90%


00:04:12.460 --> 00:04:14.905 align:middle line:84%
And I want to share
a message with you.

00:04:14.905 --> 00:04:19.320 align:middle line:90%


00:04:19.320 --> 00:04:39.570 align:middle line:84%
