are, whatever your viewpoint,

00:04:39.570 --> 00:04:50.330 align:middle line:84%
you stand in this moment of
time before a great opportunity.

00:04:50.330 --> 00:04:56.120 align:middle line:90%


00:04:56.120 --> 00:05:05.225 align:middle line:84%
