heart the language of love.

00:05:05.225 --> 00:05:15.730 align:middle line:90%


00:05:15.730 --> 00:05:28.040 align:middle line:84%
Every one of you knows in your
heart the language of beauty.

00:05:28.040 --> 00:05:38.940 align:middle line:90%


00:05:38.940 --> 00:05:47.180 align:middle line:10%
So I call you to
touch into that love

00:05:47.180 --> 00:06:00.080 align:middle line:10%
that you know, you
know it so well,

00:06:00.080 --> 00:06:14.100 align:middle line:10%
and to take it as your role,
your work, your contribution

00:06:14.100 --> 00:06:17.725 align:middle line:10%
to add to my beauty.

00:06:17.725 --> 00:06:22.950 align:middle line:90%


00:06:22.950 --> 00:06:28.350 align:middle line:84%
