place of love in your heart.

00:07:16.680 --> 00:07:28.800 align:middle line:90%


00:07:28.800 --> 00:07:32.080 align:middle line:90%
So this it's simple.

00:07:32.080 --> 00:07:34.590 align:middle line:90%


00:07:34.590 --> 00:07:36.000 align:middle line:90%
It's step by step.

00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:41.120 align:middle line:90%


00:07:41.120 --> 00:07:42.145 align:middle line:90%
It's every day.

00:07:42.145 --> 00:07:47.420 align:middle line:90%


00:07:47.420 --> 00:07:48.560 align:middle line:90%
It's every moment.

00:07:48.560 --> 00:07:58.880 align:middle line:90%


00:07:58.880 --> 00:07:59.915 align:middle line:90%
Look around you.

00:07:59.915 --> 00:08:05.310 align:middle line:90%


00:08:05.310 --> 00:08:06.855 align:middle line:90%
Are you seeing beauty?

00:08:06.855 --> 00:08:10.470 align:middle line:90%


00:08:10.470 --> 00:08:12.990 align:middle line:84%
Is there something
you can clean up?

00:08:12.990 --> 00:08:17.840 align:middle line:90%


00:08:17.840 --> 00:08:19.130 align:middle line:90%
Something you can grow?

00:08:19.130 --> 00:08:22.530 align:middle line:90%


00:08:22.530 --> 00:08:26.250 align:middle line:84%
Is there something you
can give to someone else?

00:08:26.250 --> 00:08:32.500 align:middle line:90%


00:08:32.500 --> 00:08:36.250 align:middle line:84%
Is there a little
moment of sharing?

00:08:36.250 --> 00:08:39.559 align:middle line:90%
A tiny touch?

00:08:39.559 --> 00:08:42.390 align:middle line:90%
An instant of beauty?

00:08:42.390 --> 00:08:45.300 align:middle line:90%


00:08:45.300 --> 00:08:46.180 align:middle line:90%
That's all it takes.

00:08:46.180 --> 00:08:49.460 align:middle line:90%


00:08:49.460 --> 00:09:00.436 align:middle line:84%
One moment and another
and another and another.

00:09:00.436 --> 00:09:02.490 align:middle line:90%
You know how to do this.

00:09:02.490 --> 00:09:05.140 align:middle line:90%


00:09:05.140 --> 00:09:08.230 align:middle line:90%
You know so well.

00:09:08.230 --> 00:09:24.520 align:middle line:90%


00:09:24.520 --> 00:09:27.100 align:middle line:90%
Every single one of you.

